title: Bob Dylan - Passion (1979-1987)
description:
BOB DYLAN - Passion! (1979-1987)

A representative sample of Dylan's gospel sounds, compiled from the best available sources circa 2006 (Dylan & The Dead has since been remastered).  Volume levels were adjusted for overall consistency.  I believe Dylan's work in this period is generally underrated.  If this compilation helps to alter the popular perception, it will have been worth it.  Enjoy!
